lyrics:
(chorus)
is this not he. the one who walks on the waves of the sea. who measured the waters in the hollow of his hand and calculated the heavens . Who has held the dust of the earth in a basket or weighed the mountains in a scale and the hills with a balance, GREAT and MARVELOUS are his deeds the creator, for in his hands is the life of every living thing and the breath of all mankind. ( mankind)
